snippet.title: PM Modi Launches Lucky Draw Schemes to Boost Digital Payments

localized.description:
Prime Minister Narendra Modi launches lucky draw schemes namely 'Lucky Grahak Yojana for consumers and Digi-Dhan Vyapar Yojana for merchants' to boost digital payments.
